OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779847404
OL,3,CBetting ads featuring Harry Kane and
OL,4,CErling Haaland banned
OL,6,FTwo ads for online betting platform
OL,7,FOddschecker featuring images of
OL,8,Ffootballers Harry Kane and Erling
OL,9,FHaaland have been banned for being
OL,10,Flikely to appeal to under-18s.
OL,12,FThe first Instagram post on the
OL,13,Foddscheckertv account, seen in
OL,14,FNovember, used a photo of Kane with
OL,15,Fthe caption: "Harry Kane is the most
OL,16,Fbacked player to win the Ballon d'Or
OL,17,Fin 2026 (32% of bets)," with a trophy
OL,18,Femoji.
OL,26,@wD@NOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779847404
OL,3,CBetting ads featuring Harry Kane and
OL,4,CErling Haaland banned
OL,6,FThe second featured a photo of Erling
OL,7,FHaaland and the text: "In the last 24
OL,8,Fhours, Norway to win the 2026 World
OL,9,FCup is the most-backed bet placed
OL,10,Fthrough oddschecker."
OL,12,FThe complainant, a researcher from
OL,13,FBristol University, challenged whether
OL,14,Fthe ads breached gambling advertising
OL,15,Frules for featuring individuals who
OL,16,Fwere likely to be of strong appeal to
OL,17,Funder-18s.
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779847404
OL,3,CBetting ads featuring Harry Kane and
OL,4,CErling Haaland banned
OL,6,FCyan Blue Odds Ltd, trading as
OL,7,FOddschecker, said the posts were
OL,8,F"primarily editorial in nature, rather
OL,9,Fthan ads".
OL,11,FThey explained that this was why they
OL,12,Fdid not include the age disclaimer and
OL,13,Fsocial responsibility message that
OL,14,Fwould ordinarily accompany their
OL,15,Fdirect gambling promotions.
OL,17,FThe firm said it recognised the
OL,18,Fheightened risk associated with
OL,19,Ffeaturing "top-flight" footballers and
OL,20,Fso had set the account to a minimum
OL,21,Fage of 18-plus.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@IO]{D@KOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779847404
OL,3,CBetting ads featuring Harry Kane and
OL,4,CErling Haaland banned
OL,6,FUpholding the complaint, the ASA said
OL,7,Fa large proportion of under-18s used
OL,8,FInstagram and it was likely there was
OL,9,Fat least a significant number of
OL,10,Fchildren who had not used their real
OL,11,Fdate of birth when signing up.
OL,13,FIt said it considered both Kane and
OL,14,FHaaland "to be a high risk of strong
OL,15,Fappeal to under-18s".
OL,17,FThe ASA said: "For those reasons, we
OL,18,Fconcluded the ads were irresponsible
OL,19,Fand breached the code."
OL,26,@vD@IOUwD@TO]yD@OOU{D@WO]
