OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779847404
OL,3,CBetting ads featuring Harry Kane and
OL,4,CErling Haaland banned
OL,6,FIn a separate ruling, the ASA found
OL,7,Fthat an Instagram post from Betway
OL,8,Ffeaturing an image of former Arsenal
OL,9,Fstriker Thierry Henry did not break
OL,10,Fadvertising rules because he was
OL,11,Funlikely to be of strong appeal to
OL,12,Funder-18s.
